Interface AIAgentFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
AlphaZeroPlayerFactory, MCTSPlayerFactory, RandomPlayerFactory
public interface AIAgentFactory
Factory interface for creating AI agents. Decouples agent instantiation from client code (GameController, NavigationService). Allows runtime flexibility in agent creation and configuration.
Author:
Team 04
